org.jooby.apitool.raml

Class RamlType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jooby.apitool.raml.RamlType

  • public class RamlType
extends Object
    RAML type which must be either Raml.define(Type) or Raml.define(Type). Basic types are available as static field instances: NUMBER, STRING, etc..
    Since:
    1.2.0
    Author:
    edgar
